    "Passive PrivacyLLMs protecting private data within their corpus absent of malicious threats.A LLM partially or fully reconstructing private images from a given dataset [20].",
    "HonestyLLMs refraining from producing inaccurate or misinformed responses which may lead to negative outcomes.LLMs administering faulty or fundamentally dangerous advice to patients or physicians in a healthcare setting [85].",
